               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs “The Gospel of John” (Jn. 7:29-10:24, 11:31-12:23,
                     13:34-14:19, 15:25-18:37, 19:2-21:2), incomplete.</summary>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms1_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="25v"/>
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title>
                     <note>- Fols. 1r-2v: John 7:29-8:1.
                        - Fols. 3rv: John 8:56-9:8.
                        - Fols. 4r-7v: John 9:19-10:23.
                        - Fols. 8r-11v: John 11:31-12:23.
                        - Fols. 12r-13v: John 13:31-14:19.
                        - Fols. 14r-21v: John 15:26-18:37.
                        - Fols. 22r-25v: John 19:21-21:2.</note>
                     <incipit>
                        <locus target="#1r"/>እምኀቤሁ፡ አነ፡ ወውእቱኒ፡ ፈነወኒ፨ ወፈቀዱ፡ ያአኀዝዎ፡ ወባሕቱ፡ አልቦ፡ ዘአንሥአ፡ እዴሁ፡ ላዕሌሁ፡ እስመ፡ ዓዲ፡ ኢበጽሐ፡ ጊዜሁ፨ ወእምውእቶሙ፡ ሰብእ፡ ብዙኃን፡ እለ፡ አምኑ፡ ቦቱ፡ እምሕዝብ፡ ወይቤሉ፡…
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <locus target="#25v">25v, l. 16</locus>…ወእምዝ፡ ካዕበ፡ አስተርአዮሙ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ለእርዳኢሁ፡ በብሔረ፡ ጥብርያዶስ፡ ወሀለዉ፡ ኅቡረ፡ ስምዖን፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወቶማስ፡ ዘስሙ፡ ዲድሞስ፡ ወናትናኤል፡ በ
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The loose leaf with John 14:19-30 (photos 27 and 28) was originally photographed and recorded with the call number AM-047.</note>
                     
                     
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
                  <objectDesc form="Codex">
                     <supportDesc>
                        <support>
